data.description: The wait is over! This 3,000 square foot custom built home on over 2 acres with a pool and a 900 square foot shed is ready for you. From the ''rocking chair'' front porch to the welcoming foyer, the tone is set for this warm and inviting home. Upon entry there are double doors leading to what could be an office or a formal living or dining room (the current owners use it as a home gym.) As you enter the gas fireplace adorned living room you get a cozy feel in a wideopen space. The brick accent arch offers warmth and separation while still allowing for that open concept flow. This kitchen has it all...Bosch double oven, Bosch gas stove, a large island for all your cooking and entertaining and a grand dining area. Take the party outside to the screened-in patio, complete with tongue and groove ceilings, slate tiled floors and a wood burning fireplace, all looking out over the salt water pool and massive yard for all your work and play activities. The primary suite offers vaulted ceilings, tons of natural light and an inviting on-suite. A tiled shower, double vanities and a walk in closet finish out the primary space. Jack and Jill bathrooms separate bedrooms 2 and 3, while bedroom number 4 is located on the other side of the home with a full bath nearby. Storage and staging space in the laundry room make the task just a bit more bearable. Upstairs is a giant bonus room, the possibilities are endless. A whole house natural gas generator is set for auto on and auto off, to keep you comfortable no matter what the weather. Don't wait! You could start the new year off right in your new home.
